---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Blue Fox Tours"
  description="Who we are and how we got here"
>
  <PageHeader 
    title="About Me" 
    subtitle="It's always better to know your guide. Get to know my background, qualifications and style."
    backgroundImage="/uploads/tours-header-bg.jpg"
  />
  
  <section class="section-y">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Who am I?</h2>
          <p class="text-l text-gray-700 mb-8">
            My name is Filip and I first started giving tours in 2010. Since then, I've led thousands of tours, mostly in Prague, but also in Kutná Hora, Terezín and Karlštejn.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6">What to expect on my tours?</h2>
          <p class="text-l text-gray-700 mb-8">
            I believe that a Tour Guide is an ambassador for their city and country. On my tours, I go beyond just showing you around. My goal is to help you understand our history, 
            culture and identity almost as if you actually lived here. My tours are story-oriented, factual and entertaining.
          </p>
          <p class="text-l text-gray-700 mb-8">
            Essentially, I do the kind of tours I would like to be on. Enjoyable, memorable, honest.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6">What are my qualifications?</h2>
          <p class="text-l text-gray-700 mb-8">
            I have a Bachelor's Degree in Tourism, the official Tour Guide license, as well as official qualification as Tour Guide and Guide of Prague. 
            I do tours in English at a native level (C2), and in Czech.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <img 
            src="/uploads/about-guide.jpg" 
            alt="Filip Tour Guide at Prague Castle" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover w-full h-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>